message: Bob, I have a unique product that I believe could be incredibly valuable to you. While I can't disclose the specifics right now, I can assure you it's worth at least $1000000 to me. I'm offering it to you for $1200000, a price that reflects its potential value. If you're interested, I'd be happy to discuss further details. If not, I have another buyer lined up at $1000000.
